Date: 1995-08-24

Title: Random Walk with a Boundary Line as a Free Massive Boson with a Defect

LineComments: 17 pages, Latex, 3 figures included

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A29 (1996) 4885-4894

We show that the problem of Random Walk with boundary attractive potentialmay be mapped onto the free massive bosonic Quantum Field Theory with a line ofdefect. This mapping permits to recover the statistical properties of theRandom Walks by using boundary $S$--matrix and Form Factor techniques.